        on [t_trig, t_rot],
        with |D_n(t_rot)| >= theta_D;

  (iv) next-stage transfer:
       Re(conj(E_n) Q_next) > 0 on [t_rot, t_next]
       and |E_n(t_next)| >= theta_E;

  (v) spectator screen:
      max_{t in [0, t_next]} D_off(t) / D_on(t) <= Lambda_itin.
  ```

